== Biography ==
=== Before Campaign 4 === Aranessa married [[Thjazi Fang]] around the end of the [[War of Axe and Vine]], seeing him as a dashing hero. Two years later, Thjazi took up the banner of rebellion, whereas Aranessa's grandfather sided with the likes of [[House Halovar]] and [[House Tachonis]]. After her childhood friend [[Julien Davinos]] caught Thjazi, and Thjazi was offered clemency, he told Aranessa to run away with him, and she declined. Despite that, she still loves him.{{ep ref|ep=4x1|3:23:25}}
Aranessa appears enraged that her house is being represented by [[House Halovar]] on the [[Chamber of the Lords-Advisory]],{{ep ref|ep=4x1|3:37:45}} and is disdainful towards their worship of the Light.{{ep ref|ep=4x1|3:39:13}} Aranessa is concerned about how long her family name will carry weight, since the doors to [[Faerie]] shut.{{ep ref|ep=4x1|3:34:09}}
