{{Infobox Character | title = <!-- If different from article title --> | image = | caption = <!-- Basic information --> | type = NPC | setting = Aramán | actor = Brennan Lee Mulligan | class = | species = [[Orc]] <!-- Biographical information --> | pronouns = she/her | characterTitles = | AKA = | age = <!-- Use {{character age}} --> | languages = <!-- Avoid using if the only entry is "Common" --> | place = | family = | partner = | children = | profession = Mercenary | affiliations = {{Plainlist| *[[Torn Banner]] (commander) *[[Teor Pridesire]] (companion)}} <!-- Status --> | status = Alive | deathReason = <!-- Both cause and episode/date go here. Keep this *brief* --> <!-- Mechanical information --> <!-- Appearances --> | first = {{ep|4x01}} | last = | stream = [[Campaign 4]] (1 episode) }} '''Loza Blade''' is an orc mercenary. As a [[non-player character]] in [[Campaign 4]], Loza is played by [[Brennan Lee Mulligan]].
