/www.youtube.com/watch?v=HvpF1EhOyKw|ep=Critical Role Cooldown &#124; Campaign 4, Episode 1|10:37}} As a [[non-player character]] in [[Campaign 4]], Enmity is played by [[Brennan Lee Mulligan]].
== Description == Enmity has speckled red and black skin that appears like lava congealing into stone, and ram-like horns. She wears a white priestly garb. She speaks with a growling, guttural voice.{{Ep ref|ep=4x1|1:29:13}}
=== Personality === Enmity appears to believe strongly in the [[Candescent Creed]], expressing disappointment in [[Tyranny]] for 'dimming her light' by swearing. She is also quite enthusiastic to the point of insecurity.{{Ep ref|ep=4x1|1:30:33}}
== Biography == Enmity recently came to [[Dol-Makjar]], becoming an Aspirant of the Candescent Creed.
