== Description == Pin is a small, mostly white fox made of pieces of different foxes, with purple button eyes. Its front right leg and one of its ears is from a red fox, while most of the rest of Pin's body is an arctic fox.{{ep ref|ep=4x02|1:35:08}}
He wears a purple scarf around his neck.{{ep ref|ep=4x02|1:35:23}}
=== Personality === <!-- Insert character personality here. If there is not a lot of information to dedicate sections for them, consider deleting the header and merging the section upwards.-->
Pin is playful with other animals he's familiar with, notably [[Wulferic]].{{ep ref|ep=4x01|2:43:28}}
