== Biography == === [[Campaign 4]] === Ethrand joined his father [[Primus Tachonis]] in the attack on [[Palazzo Davinos]]. Accompanied by six [[ghoul]]s, he entered the room where his brother [[Occtis]] was speaking to Lady [[Aranessa Royce]]. While under a field of ''Silence'', the ghouls restrained Occtis on a table and Ethrand stabbed him in the chest. Dropping the ''Silence'', Ethrand told his brother that there was always something wrong with him and he should've simply accepted the family name. He then carved out Occtis' heart and plunged the [[Stone of Nightsong]] into his brother's chest. Etherand then ordered the ghouls to throw Aranessa over the balcony. As Ethrand retreated he was confronted by [[Thaisha Lloy]], but escaped as Primus appeared and rescued him by ''Plane Shifting'' away.{{ep ref|ep=4x04|01:44:32}}
