{{Infobox Character <!-- Delete parameters that are unlikely to be ever filled --> | title = <!-- If different from article title --> | image = | caption = <!-- Basic information --> | type = NPC | setting = | actor = [[Brennan Lee Mulligan]] | class = | species = [[Nixie]] <!-- Biographical information --> | name = <!-- If different from article title --> | pronouns = she/her | characterTitles = | AKA = | age = <!-- Use {{character age}} --> | languages = <!-- Avoid using if the only entry is "Common" --> | place = [[Dahapshanee Wood]] | family = | partner = | children = | profession = Scout | affiliations = <!-- Major meaningful relationships and group memberships --> <!-- Status --> | status = Alive | deathReason = <!-- Both cause and episode/date go here. Keep this *brief* --> <!-- Appearances --> | first = {{ep|4x05}} | last = {{ep|4x05}} | stream = [[Campaign 4]] (1 episode) | television = | comic = | other = }} '''Brookmeadow''' is a [[nixie]] scout on the way to [[Hawthorn's Glade]]. As a [[non-player character]] in [[Campaign 4]], she is played by [[Brennan Lee Mulligan]].
== Description == Brookmeadow is about seven inches tall, and is able to breathe underwater and provide other small fairies with the same ability.{{ep ref|ep=4x05|2:40:34}}
== Biography == === [[Campaign 4]] === [[Thimble]] noticed Brookmeadow hiding in a small brook in the Dahapshanee Wood as she and her mortal companions pursued [[Cyd]]. Brookmeadow asked Thimble silently if she was in danger, and when Thimble said she wasn't, pulled her underwater and provided her in private with information out of earshot of the others: Hawthorn's Glade, a haven for [[fae]], was about a day's travel away, and a [[nama]] who seemed stressed and in a hurry had passed by the previous day.{{ep ref|ep=4x05|2:41:20}} In thanks, Thimble gave her a button.{{ep ref|ep=4x05|2:45:54}}
== Appearances and mentions == * [[Campaign 4]] ** {{appearance|4x05|appear|{{1st}}}} ** {{appearance|4x06|mention}}
